            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air, then preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into small bite-sized pieces and add them to a large <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1679590644133-x200.jpg",
