            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir in your <strong>dried basil</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong> – this is your <strong>herby stock</strong></p><p>Slice <strong>half </strong>your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon[s]</strong> into slices and set them aside for later</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1679590658211-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1679590658211-x400.jpg",
